products.title: ZOTAC GeForce GTX 1050 Ti Mini, 4GB GDDR5 DisplayPort 128-bit Gaming Graphic Card (ZT-P10510A-10L)
features: New nvidia pascal architecture delivers improved performance and power efficiency
Fast, smooth, power efficient gaming experiences
Extended warranty included. Registration required on Zotac website
products.description:
Turn Your PC Into a True Gaming Rig With the Fast, Powerful Geforce Gtx 1050 Ti. Its powered by NVIDIA Pascal the most advanced GPU architecture ever created and features innovative NVIDIA technologies to drive the latest games in their full glory in super compact solutions.


PERFORMANCE

 All new NVIDIA Pascal architecture
 Created with the latest technologies and supports DirectX12 features
 Experience super fast, smooth, power efficient gameplay


GAMING TECHNOLOGIES
 Revolutionary new professional quality in game image capture photos with NVIDIA Ansel technology
 Immerse yourself in a cinematic experience utilizing NVIDIA GameWorks and GSYNC technologies


SPECIFICATIONS

 NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050 Ti GPU
 768 CUDA cores
 4GB GDDR5 memory
 128 bit memory bus
 Engine clock (base): 1303 MHz (boost): 1417 MHz
 Memory clock: 7.0 GHz
 PCI Express 3.0


CONNECTIONS

 1 x DisplayPort 1.4
 1 x HDMI 2.0b
 1 x Dual link DVI
 Triple simultaneous display capable


POWER REQUIREMENTS

 300 watt power supply recommended
 75 watt max power consumption


SOFTWARE COMPATIBILITY

 NVIDIA GeForce driver
 Microsoft DirectX 12 (feature level 12_1)
 OpenGL 4.5
 OpenCL
 Microsoft Windows 10/8/7 x86/x64


DIMENSIONS

 Card Length: 144.78mm (5.7 in)
 Card Height: 111.15mm (4.38 in)
 Card Width: Dual slots
 Box Height: 280mm (11.02in), Width: 215mm (8.46in), Depth: 55mm (2.17in)


INSIDE THE BOX

 ZOTAC GeForce GTX 1050 Ti
 User Manual
